snippet.title: ABC Sports Indy Racing Gameplay
snippet.description:
ABC Sports Indy Racing is the only CD-ROM game that allows gamers to choose from eight authentic Indy tracks and four driving modules and place Indy Racing League drivers in their official team cars. This is the only authorized guide to the game, and it will feature exclusive material from Paul Page and Tom Sniva as they coach players throughout.
